snippet.title: Captain MaCaw - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for Captain MaCaw.

An old school platform adventure game in the style of the ZX Spectrum, coming soon to Steam for Windows.

Available on or before Feb 18th 2019.

http://auld-games.co.uk/
https://store.steampowered.com/app/946000/Captain_MaCaw/
https://twitter.com/Auldgames
https://www.facebook.com/auldgames/
